STATEMENT: >>>
This section constitutes the Software Change Records as required by
EN 50716:2023, Clause 9.2 and Table A.1 (document 43). One DCR-xxx entry
shall be completed for each approved change, from change request through to
verification closure. Duplicate the change record template for each change.
