[TEXT]
STATEMENT: >>>
This section constitutes the Software Maintenance Verification Report as
required by EN 50716:2023, Clause 9.2 and Table A.1 (document 45). It records
the results of independent verification of each maintenance cycle, confirming
that changes were implemented and tested in accordance with the Software
Maintenance Plan (§5) and that the safety integrity of the software is
maintained.
